      "description": "Available now is a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in impeccable condition. This chassis is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and Double-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the factory M-Variable Differential Lock. This vehicle has undergone rigorous preventative maintenance, including documented rod bearing replacement and structural subframe reinforcement. Every bushing is tight, the suspension geometry is true, and the hydraulic steering rack provides unparalleled feedback. Finished in factory-original paint with a flawless interior, this is a turn-key example of the ultimate driving machine.",
      "price": 48500.0,
