      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, the exterior is absolutely flawless\u2014free of rock chips, door dings, or even the slightest swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is supple and completely devoid of wear or creasing, and the interior retains its original, crisp scent. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity surround sound system to the advanced driver assistance suite, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained by certified technicians with a comprehensive, documented service history. It has been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a meticulously preserved example for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than a showroom-perfect experience.",
